Package coreservlets

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    deleteFilm
    The public 'deleteFilm' servlet class sets up a HTTP route for deleting a film record from the database, using doGet.
    FilmList  
    getAllFilms
    The public 'getAllFilms' servlet class sets up a HTTP route for getting an ArrayList of all films from the database, and displaying it in a web browser, using doGet and doPost.
    getFilm
    The public 'getFilm' servlet class sets up a HTTP route for getting an ArrayList of films with a title that matches a given title input string, and displaying it in a web browser, using doGet and doPost.
    insertFilm
    The public 'insertFilm' servlet class sets up a HTTP route for inserting a film record into the database, using doGet.
    updateFilm
    The public 'updateFilm' servlet class sets up a HTTP route for updating an existing film record in the database, using doGet.
